## Three channel adapters

**Email (SendGrid / AWS SES):** Best for rich content — weekly earnings digests, KYC approval letters, payout receipts. Use HTML templates with your design system colors. Respect CAN-SPAM: include unsubscribe footer on all marketing-class emails.

**WhatsApp (Twilio or Meta Cloud API):** Must use pre-approved message templates for outbound initiated messages (Meta's requirement). Best for time-sensitive, action-required events: private show requests, urgent KYC decisions. Require users to opt-in with their WhatsApp number in profile settings.

**Push / In-app (FCM + APNs):** Best for real-time, glanceable alerts — go-live events, tip received, room announcements. Store FCM/APNs device tokens per user in PostgreSQL. Also power the in-app bell icon (WebSocket fan-out to the live room).

